videos.headline: Armstead's 56-yard dash has Temple in red zone
videos.description: Ryquell Armstead takes the handoff and runs for 56 yards and puts the Owls in the red zone.

videos.headline: Palmer's 23-yard catch sparks UMass offense
videos.description: Andrew Ford hits Sadiq Palmer for a 23-yard gain moving the Minutemen towards midfield.

videos.headline: Young's stiff arm spurs long run, puts UMass on doorstep
videos.description: UMass RB Marquis Young breaks multiple tackles and takes the ball all the way to the Temple six-yard line.

videos.headline: Marchi escapes pressure to complete 19-yard pass
videos.description: Temple QB Logan Marchi avoids the UMass pass rushers and throws a laser to complete the 19-yard pass to Keith Kirkwood.

videos.headline: UMass blocks Temple FG, keeps game within 3
videos.description: UMass' Isaiah Rodgers comes off the edge and blocks the 43-yard field attempt by Temple K Austin Jones.

videos.headline: Isabella tightropes the sideline on a 36-yard deep ball
videos.description: UMass QB Andrew Ford completes the 36-yard pass to Andy Isabella along the sideline to put UMass on the Temple 25-yard line.

videos.headline: Ford TD to Orekoya puts UMass ahead
videos.description: UMass QB Andrew Ford completes the 10-yard pass to Nick Orekoya for the UMass touchdown.

videos.headline: Wright makes tackler miss, gets ball into UMass territory
videos.description: Temple QB Logan Marchi completes a pass to Isaiah Wright who makes a man miss for a 25-yard reception.

videos.headline: Temple answers back with 30-yard TD pass
videos.description: Temple QB Logan Marchi completes a 30-yard touchdown pass on the run to Adonis Jennings on the run for the touchdown.

videos.headline: UMass QB fumbles, gives Temple ball back inside red zone
videos.description: Temple's Quincy Roche strip sacks UMass QB Andrew Ford and recovers the fumble on the UMass 18-yard line.

videos.headline: Temple scores 2nd TD in 54 seconds
videos.description: The Owls capitalize on a fumble, and Temple QB Logan Marchi tosses an 11-yard touchdown pass to Keith Kirkwood.

videos.headline: Marchi hooks up with Kirkwood for another big play
videos.description: Temple QB Logan Marchi completes a 30 yard pass to Keith Kirkwood moving Owls to the UMass 46-yard line.

videos.headline: Ford's 20 yard strike to Britt cuts Temple lead
videos.description: UMass QB Andrew Ford connects with Jesse Britt for a 20-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Armstead's 20 yard scamper puts Temple in the red zone
videos.description: Temple RB Ryquell Armstead cuts up field and runs for a 20 yard gain putting the Owls inside the red zone.

videos.headline: Ford hits Britt for another big play
videos.description: UMass QB Andrew Ford hits Jessie Britt with a strike good for 25 yards and puts the Minutemen at the Temple 28-yard line.

videos.headline: Wright shakes defenders; takes Temple into red zone
videos.description: Temple QB Logan Marchi hits Isaiah Wright with a short pass and Wright breaks multiple tackles moving the Owls to the UMass 18-yard line.

videos.headline: Wright's one-handed TD grab gives Temple breathing room
videos.description: Temple QB Logan Marchi pass complete to Isaiah Wright who makes one-handed catch for the 13-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Dingle makes tough one-handed catch on 37 yard pass
videos.description: UMass QB Andrew Ford tosses a 37-yard strike to Brennon Dingle, who makes a one-handed catch that brings Minutemen to the Temple 29-yard line.

videos.headline: Ford leaps into the end zone; pulls UMass within eight
videos.description: UMass QB Andrew Ford takes the snap and turns the corner diving inside the pylon for the touchdown.
